            "text": "Aloha Wear for over 60 years",
            "size": "h3"
          }
        },
        "text_yW3FNF": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>From our humble beginnings on the island of Kauai and the International Marketplace in Waikiki, Hilo Hattie has become synonymous with vacation shopping. With our online store and Hilo Hattie stores on Oahu, Maui, Kona, and Kauai, locals and visitors alike can enjoy a wonderful and wide assortment of Hawaiian fashions, tees, gifts, souvenirs, home and beach accessories, beauty products, gourmet foods and stunning island jewelry.<br/><br/>Founded in 1963, Hilo Hattie has grown from one store into a chain of five stores to become Hawaii’s largest retailer, manufacturer and wholesaler of Hawaiian fashions and gifts. Voted by Hawaii's residents as \"The Best Place for Hawaiian Fashions\" for the past 10 years, Hilo Hattie guarantees our shoppers the best values, largest selection of Made-in-Hawaii gifts and a 100% quality guarantee on thousands of Hawaiian products.</p>",
            "custom_liquid": "",
            "size": "text-size-regular"
          }
        }
